{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC05_KEI_720.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x14,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "I headed over to Hornheim for the time being...but I wonder how I should look for that big slag..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Maybe I should ask someone about it...<CR>A good source of information is..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Mix Master, have you heard any news about anyone seeing a big slag around here?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "A big slag? Nooope, I haven't, but there aren't a lot of people around here to begin with..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "This slag you're talking about,<CR>how big is it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Let's see... He's like as big as a mountain..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0x140,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "A mountain? If something that big was crawling around, I'm sure someone would've noticed it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "But, it flies, since it has wings."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa2,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Seriously? A slag as big as a mountain that flies...? Oh, could it be that?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "It probably is! Please tell me about it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xab,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "A little while back, there were a few days where it was unseasonably foggy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa3,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "All the regular balloon services were stopped, but the cancellation period for the flights was so long..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa3,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "That one balloon eventually flew into the fog..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa3,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Rumor has it someone said they saw a giant in the clouds."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa6,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "It was decided that it must've just been a shadow of an island seen through the fog, but it might've been a flying slag."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, that is possible.<CR>Do you know where it was?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa8,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I don't know too much about it,<CR>but looking from here, I can tell<CR>you it was on the opposite shore."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xc,
            "name_id": 0xc,
            "extra_id": 0xa9,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "But with the dense fog and the distance, the witness's story was pretty vague."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Okay. Thank you so much."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "(Yeah, that has to be it. I should go search the other side of the valley.)"
        }
    ]
}